// savoury: adjective UK (US savory) 1. 鹹的；辛辣的 2. 令人愉快的；名聲好的；受歡迎的
a savoury dish/sauce/flavour
帶鹹味的一道菜／一種調料／一種味道
That hotel doesn't have a very savoury reputation.
