// barley: noun [ U ] 大麥
Farmers in the area grow a wide range of crops but major crops include wheat, barley, and horse beans.
該地區的農民種植多種農作物，但主要農作物包括小麥、大麥和馬豆。

// townsfolk: noun [ plural ] (also townspeople) 鎮民；市民
The townsfolk have embraced the summer music festival.
